Package: TradeRa
Title: Performing Search Queries with the Tradera API in R
Description: This R package offers functionality for accessing the Tradera API, 
    enabling users to perform search queries. This package is a part of the 
    coursework for the Advanced Programming in R course  (732A94) at Linköping 
    University.
